(0,0)
An Ogive has a horizontal x-axis labeled Age from 44.5 to 86 in increments of 5 and a vertical y-axis labeled Cumulative Frequency from 0 to 28 in increments of 4. The graph consists of seven plotted points connected by line segments from left to right. The coordinates of the plotted points are at (49.5, 0), (54.5, 6), (59.5, 2), (64.5, 24), (69.5, 21), (74.5, 11), (79.5, 19).
